- `devDependencies`: `{ "openclaw": "workspace:*" }`
- `peerDependencies`: `{ "openclaw": ">=2026.4.1-beta.1" }` (optional)
- `openclaw` block:
  - `extensions`: `["./index.ts"]`
  - `setupEntry`: `"./setup-entry.ts"`
  - `install.npmSpec`: `"@openclaw/pulseboard"`, `minHostVersion: ">=2026.4.1"`
  - `release.publishToNpm`: `true`
  - `channel`: id `"pulseboard"`, label `"PulseBoard"`, selectionLabel `"PulseBoard (API Key)"`, docsPath `"/channels/pulseboard"`, blurb `"Real-time bulletin boards and DMs."`, order `60`, `quickstartAllowFrom: true`

### Step 3: `index.ts`

